& [LMStudioCorpusPrompt:boundary_delineation_010_retry_002] is a non-mutating SOP worker prompt packet
  + [task_family] is boundary_delineation
  + [prompt_boundary] is prompt-only, no tools, no file reads, no repo mutation, no hidden-state claims
  + [expected_output] is exactly one raw SOP node named InferenceJobResult with seven filled property lines and no Markdown
  + [validation_required_fields] is focus, inside, boundary, outside, inference, caution, next_step
  + [validation_required_terms] is focus, boundary, outside, caution
